---
import AppShell from "../../layouts/AppShell.astro";
---

<AppShell activePath="/contact" pageTitle="Contact | Kaka Ruto" pageDescription="How to send a strong cold email to Kaka Ruto.">
  <section class="min-h-screen border-x border-zinc-800 bg-black/95 px-5 py-8 pb-20 lg:pb-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black leading-tight text-zinc-50">Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-300">
        Knowing how to send a great cold email is a superpower. Also, if your email starts with
        “Hope this finds you well,” it has already found the archive.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-zinc-100">The best emails:</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <li>2-3 sentences, reads like a text.</li>
          <li>Has one clear ask.</li>
          <li>Thoughtfully personalized.</li>
          <li>Punchy subject line.</li>
          <li>Avoid vague asks like “pick your brain.”</li>
          <li>Does not look like AI wrote it.</li>
          <li>No signature.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-zinc-100">Subject line examples</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <li>“Quick build collaboration idea”</li>
          <li>“Can you help me ship this in 2 weeks?”</li>
          <li>“Tiny ask on product architecture”</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-zinc-100">Mini template</h3>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 p-3 text-xs leading-6 text-zinc-300">Hi Kaka - [specific thing I noticed].

I am working on [one-line context].
Would you be open to [clear ask] this week?</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <button id="copy-email" type="button" class="rounded-full bg-sky-500 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-sky-400">
          Copy contact email
        </button>
        <a id="open-email" class="rounded-full border border-zinc-700 px-5 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-200 hover:border-zinc-500" href="#">
          Open email app
        </a>
        <p id="contact-status" class="text-sm text-zinc-400"></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script is:inline>
      const emailParts = ["contact", "kakaruto", "com"];
      const email = emailParts.join(".");
      const contactEmail = email.replace(".", "@").replace(".com", ".com");

      const status = document.getElementById("contact-status");
      const openEmail = document.getElementById("open-email");
      const subject = encodeURIComponent("Quick idea");
      const body = encodeURIComponent("Hi Kaka -\\n\\n[Your short, clear message here]\\n");

      openEmail?.setAttribute("href", `mailto:${contactEmail}?subject=${subject}&body=${body}`);

      document.getElementById("copy-email")?.addEventListener("click", async () => {
        try {
          await navigator.clipboard.writeText(contactEmail);
          status.textContent = `Copied ${contactEmail}`;
        } catch {
          status.textContent = `Email: ${contactEmail}`;
        }
      });
    </script>
  </section>
</AppShell>
